Citation.sTitle: Molar excess enthalpies of ethyl acetate + alkanols at T=298.15K, p=10MPa
Citation.sAbstract: A commercial flow-mixing isothermal calorimeter was tested by measuring heat of mixing curves for exothermic, endothermic, S-shaped and double minimum molar excess enthalpy mixtures at high pressure. The results show this calorimeter is able to produce good quality data. Molar excess enthalpies for ethyl acetate mixed with a series of simple alkanols were measured at T=298.15K and p=10MPa
